175 A.3d 155 MARGARET BELL, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. RICHARD C. KLEIN, ESQUIRE, RICHARD C. KLEIN, P.C., AND SPECTOR, GADON & ROSEN, DEFENDANTS-PETITIONERS.

C-244 September Term 2017

079865 October 26, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003523-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
